@startuml
title Flusso Project/Task API - GET /v1/projects/{projectId}/tasks

actor Client as C
participant "ProjectTask BS (borepurposingmgmt)" as API_BS
participant "ProjectTask MS (meRepurposingReg)" as API_MS
database "Database" as DB

C -> API_BS : GET /v1/projects/{projectId}/tasks
activate API_BS


note right of API_BS
HTTP_METHOD = GET
CONTENT_TYPE = application/json
end note

API_BS -> API_MS : GET {meRepurposingRegEndPoint}/v1/projects/{projectId}/tasks
activate API_MS

API_MS -> DB : Query di ricerca dei Tasks associati al projectId con i filtri indicati
DB --> API_MS : Tasks trovati / errore
API_MS --> API_BS : - JSON Response 200 OK : WrapperTaskDTOResponse { items[] } \n- Error Response 400 / 404 / 500
deactivate API_MS

API_BS --> C : - 200 OK (JSON Response) \n- 400 / 404 / 500 Error Response
deactivate API_BS

@enduml
